Package: sarcDash
Title: Sarcopenia Study Data Dashboard
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Sarcopenia",
           family = "Team",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "team@sarcopenia.study")
Description: Production-ready interactive Shiny dashboard for exploring cleaned
    Sarcopenia study data with comprehensive filtering, domain-specific analysis,
    longitudinal tracking (0-3 visits), quality checks, CSV upload, and bilingual
    support (EN/HE with RTL). Scales to 200 patients with performance optimizations.
